According to José, the victim didn't check out of the account.
"She just activated her private regime."
Then he explains a series of steps to set the account safely.
Unlike Jorge, this boy would have published photos of people he knew in unpleasant or embarrassing situations.
"Of course I'd do it if I had a problem with someone or I just wanted to.
